                                   <strong>General Provisions</strong><br>
                                   <p>
                                        This personal data processing policy has been drawn up in accordance with the requirements of the Federal Law of July 27, 2006. № 152-FЗ "On personal data" and determines the procedure for processing personal data and measures to ensure the security of personal data https://localhost:44366/ (hereinafter - the Operator).
