                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                             This Operator's policy regarding the processing of personal data (hereinafter referred to as the Policy) applies to all information that the Operator can obtain about visitors to the website <a href="https://localhost:44366/">https://localhost:44366/</a>.
                                        </li>
                                   </ol>
                              </li>
                              <li>
                                   <strong>Basic concepts used in the Policy</strong><br>
